description:
Are you built for this moment?
This is a #short clip from Pastor Alexander Bryant's message, "Is the Church Built For This News of Hope?”, https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oE9iRFcljjk&list=PL-k2Gb-DBYo9tb9fHW_AxGxJ1R8MpNnpa&index=5  teaches us that we must proclaim the everlasting gospel, the Three Angels' Messages, to provide hope to the world and to help people live better lives, just as Jesus did while He walked this earth. 
Watch the video to be reminded that we are built for this moment, built to enlighten the world about the message of truth and help them receive the abundant life God has planned for them.

—---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The Seventh-day Adventist Church has been an established denomination since 1863. It is a global Christian family with over 21 million members who hold the Bible as the ultimate authority. We are believers who promise to help people understand the Bible to find freedom, healing, and hope in Jesus.

Want to learn more about the Seventh-day Adventist Church? 
Visit our website at: https://www.adventist.org/
